description.en: TetherBlack is a revolutionary bsc project run by a team of dedicated and honest individuals. At TetherBlack we strive for safety, reliability and security which we plan on bringing into the bsc space. This will be the first of many projects of our ecosystem and will be heavily funded by taxes of the other projects. Determined project owners can purchase franchises of our ecosystem with ease and in a secure way in which they will carry our name to success.
